	column 'Stock Status Sort' = ```
			
			SWITCH(
			    TRUE(),
			    'analytics current_stock'[Total_Stock] <= 0, 4, 
			    'analytics current_stock'[Total_Stock] <= 100, 3,
			    'analytics current_stock'[Total_Stock] <= 200, 2,
			    'analytics current_stock'[Total_Stock] > 300, 1
			)
			```
		formatString: 0
		lineageTag: 2da96e8f-f9b3-49cf-9b83-9c5b754dfd1e
		summarizeBy: sum

		annotation SummarizationSetBy = Automatic

